  "diagram_type": "sequence",
  "code": "sequenceDiagram\n    Git Client->>+LoadBalancer: HTTPS GET /\n    LoadBalancer->>+NGINX: HTTP(S) GET /\n    NGINX->>+Workhorse: HTTP GET /\n    Workhorse->>+Puma: HTTP GET /\n    Puma->>-Workhorse: 200 OK\n    Workhorse->>+Gitaly: gRPC Request\n\n    Gitaly->>+Workhorse: Auth Verify\n    Workhorse->>+Puma: Auth Confirm\n    Puma->>-Workhorse: Auth OK\n    Workhorse->>-Gitaly: Auth OK\n\n    Gitaly->>-Workhorse: gRPC Response\n    Workhorse->>-NGINX: HTTP Response\n    NGINX->>-LoadBalancer: HTTP Response\n    LoadBalancer->>-Git Client: HTTP Response",
  "content_size": 542,
  "collected_at": "2026-02-06T10:57:07.060524",
  "compilation_status": "success",
  "license": "gitlab_repo",
  "license_name": "GitLab Repository (refer to project page)",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下Git客户端请求仓库首页的完整链路。用户从Git Client发起HTTPS GET请求，先经过LoadBalancer，然后到NGINX，再往下流转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Git Client",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "HTTPS GET"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，LoadBalancer到NGINX这里，协议是HTTP还是HTTPS？有些场景LB会卸载SSL。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "HTTP(S)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "标成HTTP(S)吧，两种情况都兼容。NGINX后面接的是Workhorse，然后Workhorse再调Puma。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NGINX",
        "Workhorse",
        "Puma"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，NGINX到Workhorse是HTTP GET，Workhorse到Puma也是HTTP GET。Puma返回200 OK给Workhorse。这里Workhorse还需要访问Gitaly吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NGINX",
        "Workhorse",
        "Puma",
        "Gitaly",
        "200 OK",
        "HTTP GET"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Workhorse发gRPC Request给Gitaly。但这里有个关键细节——Gitaly要先做Auth Verify，确认权限。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Workhorse",
        "Gitaly",
        "gRPC Request",
        "Auth Verify"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Auth Verify的流程是Gitaly直接回给Workhorse，然后Workhorse再去找Puma确认吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gitaly",
        "Workhorse",
        "Puma",
        "Auth Verify",
        "Auth Confirm"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Workhorse把Auth Confirm发给Puma，Puma返回Auth OK，然后Workhorse再把Auth OK回给Gitaly，这样Gitaly才返回gRPC Response。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Workhorse",
        "Puma",
        "Gitaly",
        "Auth Confirm",
        "Auth OK",
        "gRPC Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，最后响应链路是Workhorse回NGINX，NGINX回LoadBalancer，再到Git Client。整个双向流程都画好了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Workhorse",
        "NGINX",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "Git Client",
        "HTTP Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
